	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="/db/item.html?item=2003&amp;mid=111645913111135">Brothers gonna work it out</a> <a id="fs8" href="/db/item.html?item=2003&amp;mid=111645913111135#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Wed, May 18th 7:30 PM 2005</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=600782"><span id=" ">Nidachi</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">10 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>I killed Brother Zephyl the other day. He dropped the Robe for me first time around. Got my monks epic in a day. Went back to kill Brother Zephyl in Rathe Mountains, just to get the robe again. This time i have killed him a total of (5 times), and Brother Quinn(2 times) in Southern Karana... both of them are dropping Cloth Tunic and headband only. Both of them max hit for 356points. <br/><br/>New info:Killed Brother Zephyl again this morning. He dropped the Robe of Lost Circles again. This time i noticed that the First Brother Zephyl that i killed that morning before at around 2:30Am, dropped the robe also. So both times i killed him at around 2:30Am he dropped robe....but all the other times that i killed him, he dropped headband, torn cloth tunic,and sometimes human blood. <br/><br/>Oh btw....was kinda strange, while tanking him with my Ranger i saw Brother Zephyl wearing a red robe.....but on my Cleric, he wasnt. That happened both times i killed him, when he dropped the ROLC. <br/><br/>Chars Used: 70 Ranger max tracking and logged my 70 Cleric when Brother Zephyl respawned. <br/><br/>Location of camp: -548.17, 746.66, 16.30(Brother Zephyl, Rathe Mountains) and Brother Qwinn was wondering around South Karana. <br/><br/><br/>Mobs killed: A drake (lvl 25ish), Hasten Bootstrutter (lvl 40), Maldyn the Unkempt (lvl 35ish), Brother Zephyl (lvl 61) <br/><br/>Personal Opinion: Kill Brothers until you get Robe of Lost Circles. Really no points in doing Sub quest for it. Seems some people have put some serious hours into that quest. <br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>As far as the pipes. I camped Karnors for 30mins and got pipe..camped Chardok with my girlfriend and killed a Iksar Betrayer on second spawn.. <br/><br/>I went back to get pipes again right after i got Celestial Fist. Same exact thing happen to me ..this time i waited a little longer for Karnors (Pawduster) to spawn,&nbsp;&nbsp;both times i seen him spawn in Warlords room, he spawned 3rd mob from the door. <br/><br/>Well i hope this information will help the next guy that kills either brother. <br/><br/></p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />(70 Exarch Cleric) (70 Hunter Ranger) (70 Veteran Pally) (57 Monk) (Server: Cazic)</td></tr>
