 is for the weak and impatient.  I will not MQ the Chardok and KC pipes, and I will not in any way MQ my epic.  MQing/buying the components are signs of sure weakness.  For you Iksar Monks, take the punishment for being a hated race, work on faction, do the headband quests yourself you lazy pieces o' crap!  I have said what I wanted, flame away.<br/><br/>Gesthal Vecter - Current 44 Monk of Xegony.<br/>(Wow, that was long ;)</p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Taelian<br/>THF/RDM<br/>Diabolos</td></tr>
